Singkirkan.

36
00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:47.080
Kenapa?

37
00:03:48.200 --> 00:03:49.830
Aku bilang singkirkan.

38
00:03:51.160 --> 00:03:53.710
Adipati, jangan malu-malu.

39
00:03:55.110 --> 00:03:57.270
Nanti tidak manjur
kalau kayunya habis terbakar.

40
00:03:57.270 --> 00:03:57.710
Ayo.

41
00:04:03.320 --> 00:04:04.880
Terima kasih.

42
